title: The Plant Cafe Organic - Embarcadero Pier 3
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic food cafe and restaurant with 3 locations in San Francisco. Offers an extensive menu featuring raw juices, smoothies, soups, panini sandwiches and veggie burgers, Asian-style main entrees, and American cuisine. The sit-down restaurant is across from the takeaway. Has vegan baked goods (cookies, muffins), Blue Bottle Coffee. Brunch on Sunday.
